  <diagram name="filter_flow">
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as React UI
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Perceptron as RAG Engine
    participant DynamoDB
    participant OpenSearch

    User-&gt;&gt;UI: Apply Filters
    UI-&gt;&gt;API: Send Filter Request
    API-&gt;&gt;Perceptron: Query with Filters
    Perceptron-&gt;&gt;DynamoDB: Fetch Metadata
    Perceptron-&gt;&gt;OpenSearch: Vector Search
    OpenSearch--&gt;&gt;Perceptron: Results
    DynamoDB--&gt;&gt;Perceptron: Metadata
    Perceptron--&gt;&gt;API: Filtered Results
    API--&gt;&gt;UI: Display Results
</diagram>
